N'echiche ndï ''traditional'' Igbo, Chukwu bụ eze ndï chi na ndï uwa. Aha ya nonyere "chi" la "ukwu". Chukwu bụ onye mere he lile (chi- n'eke). Ka bụ nke ana-kpo ya ''[[Chineke]]'' ugbua. Chukwu abughi nwoke, abughi nwanyï. Mgbe ndï bekee bïara, nwe kporo Chukwu chi nke ndi Christian, me ya nke nwoke.

Ka bụ nke ndï Igbo nnuku bụ Christians ugbua.

